            "title": "港股開跌124點  吉利逆升逾4%  普拉達揚7.63%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指競價時段報20557點，跌124點或0.6%，恒生國企指數開報7638點，跌30點或0.39% ; 恒生科技指數開報4787點，升25點或0.54%，大市成交37.54億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">普拉達(01913)升7.63%，報51.5元，成交入20大。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創科(00669)挫3.74%，報73.35元 ; 聯想(00992)跌2.86%，報7.8元</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">吉利(00175)盈喜，升4.02%，報15.52元。比亞迪(01211)升0.29%，報345.2元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">攜程(09961)挫4.55%，報427.8元。</p>\n</div>",
